snippet.title: Amber Heard Gets SLAMMED for Not Wearing a Mask
snippet.description:
Amber Heard Gets SLAMMED for Not Wearing a Mask In Istanbul

SUBSCRIBE FOR MORE : http://bit.ly/32rc7vI
____________________________________________

Amber Heard is definitely keeping a watch on the hate she's been receiving online during a vacation to the Middle Eastern country. The actress has been sightseeing in the Turkish city of Istanbul over the last several days, and her visit has definitely been kicking up controversy with those who feel the actress has been disrespectful with her lack of clothes, including a face mask.
